Adds_Noble Noggin_Status_Benoggined_Desc: Crowned with a weighty mascot noggin, reducing movement speed and inhibiting the use of actions.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Area Of Infl: Area of effect for actions is expanded.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Ghostly Guis: An incorporeal form is enabling you to pass through obstacles, but additional damage is taken from certain attacks.
ContentDesc_Mahrlingen-Promenade: Dreamborough─a district of Living Memory long thought lost to interdimensional fusion─rises from the rift after decades of disconnection. Yet what lies beyond its gates is not the dazzling paradise of Constancy's memory, but a land marred by shadow and haunted by vestiges of the Endless who once called it home. You must venture into the twisted grounds and quell the lost souls' agony once and for all...but the phantoms within do not take kindly to the living.
Instancecontenttextdata_38306_Text: Bow down to my flawless noggin─your king decrees it!
Instancecontenttextdata_38307_Text: Join us, and be crowned in splendor!
Instancecontenttextdata_38308_Text: I-Impossible! You would deny my regal, royal headness!?
Instancecontenttextdata_38309_Text: Behold! Your noggin is made new!
Instancecontenttextdata_38310_Text: Little lords! Little ladies! Let us proffer our heads in friendship!
Instancecontenttextdata_38312_Text: I-Inconceivable! Why must you refuse our companionship!?
Instancecontenttextdata_38313_Text: A most splendid noggin! You are worthy of my court!
Instancecontenttextdata_38314_Text: Oh, little lords and ladies...your king has need of you!
Instancecontenttextdata_38319_Text: A pristine noggin indeed... But you mustn't let its beauty go to your head! Ohoho!
Instancecontenttextdata_38320_Text: I shall not rest until my every subject bears a beauteous noggin!
Instancecontenttextdata_38322_Text: Ah, yes... A glorious, noddling noodle, as befits my kingdom!
Instancecontenttextdata_38323_Text: Apologies for breaking character, but...perhaps it's time you stopped resisting? There are limits to my patience.
Instancecontenttextdata_38325_Text: <sob> Please, just...let me kill you! LET ME KILL YOU!
Instancecontenttextdata_38326_Text: Greetings, goodly guests! Your tea awaits!
Instancecontenttextdata_38327_Text: I've not had company in ages... This calls for my finest cups!
Instancecontenttextdata_38328_Text: Cheers! A frightful toast to you and yours!
Instancecontenttextdata_38334_Text: Round and round, the cups shall go!Where they stop? Why, no one knows!
Instancecontenttextdata_38335_Text: Drink all you like─I guarantee my brew is to die for!
Instancecontenttextdata_38337_Text: 'Tis our duty to seize the nogginless!
Instancecontenttextdata_38338_Text: Yesterday is gone, yet tomorrow never comes... So sleep, child, and drown in nightmares everlasting.
Instancecontenttextdata_38340_Text: Defy me as you wish. It will not wake you from this misery.
Instancecontenttextdata_38343_Text: Spirits of eternal reverie, to me!
Instancecontenttextdata_38344_Text: Allow me to offer my aid! Step into the light, and become as a ghost to pass through all things corporeal!
Instancecontenttextdata_38345_Text: But ware Träumerei's magicks... Should you sense danger, return to my beacons, and your mortal flesh shall be restored!
Instancecontenttextdata_38354_Text: You have entered the Endless House... Fear not, for I shall guide you through its haunted halls.
Instancecontenttextdata_38355_Text: You are a formidable slayer of ghosts...but have you the strength to best their master?
Instancecontenttextdata_38356_Text: Beyond this hall lies Träumerei, Lord of Nightmares.
Instancecontenttextdata_38357_Text: Heed my words, and together, we shall end his reign of terror!
Npcyell_14016_Text: Come out, come out, my animal friends!
Npcyell_14017_Text: Oh, how the skywheel rises! But I wish to see it fall!
Npcyell_14018_Text: We mustn't let the dolls miss out on the fun!
Npcyell_14019_Text: We've plenty of presents for you...
